text: Ðis sind þa landgemæra to Hanige.

Ærest on þa ealdan dic æt þæm heafod stoccan &lang dic on waneting<../images/tbar.gif>&lang streames on þone readan mære on cylle riþe þonne went it ðær est<../images/tbar.gif>&lang streames oð hit scyt on oeccene<../images/tbar.gif>&lang oeccene oð hit scyt on ealdan wæneting.

Þonne went it dær uuest &lang stræmes oð hit scyt on snoddan fleot midde weardne þonne went hit<../images/tbar.gif>west on þa heafda<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymð on þone smalan weg<../images/tbar.gif>endlang weges oð hit gæð eft on þa ealdan dic.
